{:itonami.blueprint/id "cloud-itonami-isic-2211"
 :itonami.blueprint/name "Manufacture of rubber tyres and tubes"
 :itonami.blueprint/isic-rev5 "2211"
 :itonami.blueprint/domain :rubber-tyre/manufacturing
 :itonami.blueprint/license "AGPL-3.0-or-later"
 :itonami.blueprint/social-impact [:worker-safety :road-safety :materials-safety]
 :itonami.blueprint/governor :tyre-plant-operations-governor
 :itonami.blueprint/robotics true
 :itonami.blueprint/required-technologies [:robotics :identity :forms :dmn :bpmn :audit-ledger :cae :cfd]
 :itonami.blueprint/status :public-oss
 :itonami.blueprint/maturity :implemented
 :itonami.blueprint/implemented-slice
 "TyreAdvisor ⊣ Tyre Plant Operations Governor, langgraph-clj
 StateGraph, append-only audit ledger. A plant OPERATIONS COORDINATION
 actor for rubber tyre and tube manufacturing (compounding/building/
 curing/vulcanization lines producing finished tyres) -- not direct
 building/curing-line-equipment control authority and not DOT/ECE
 tyre-safety certification authority. Four ops
 (`:log-production-batch` / `:schedule-maintenance` /
 `:flag-safety-concern` / `:coordinate-shipment`), all `:effect
 :propose` only. Twelve concrete governor checks elaborate this
 blueprint's four HARD invariants: propose-only effect, closed op
 allowlist, closed proposal-effect allowlist (no direct building/
 curing-line-equipment control), permanent curing-line-actuate block,
 permanent safety-certification-authority block (this actor never
 self-issues a DOT/ECE tyre-safety certification), independent
 equipment verification/registration before maintenance scheduling,
 independent batch verification/registration before shipment
 coordination, independent shipment-quantity recompute against the
 batch's own logged production quantity, double-schedule guard, tyre-
 category validation, load-index plausibility validation, and defect-
 rate plausibility validation. Safety-concern flagging (curing-defect/
 DOT-compliance/equipment-safety) ALWAYS escalates to a human plant
 supervisor; `:log-production-batch` is the only op eligible to
 auto-commit, and only at phase 3 when governor-clean."}
